"{\"uid\": \"hellomagazine.com-healthandbeauty-mother-and-baby-709863-tom-daley-sons-phoenix-robbie-paris-olympic-matching-tshirts\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Tom Daley's husbandDustin Lance Blackheld back tears as the British diver secured his fifth Olympic medal at the2024 Paris Olympicson Monday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 141, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 9, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.468679538594427e-45, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 60, \"end\": 67, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9679131264269356, \"rank\": 0.019508732269586077, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 117, \"end\": 122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997774391679, \"rank\": 2.2256091019373594e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"An incredible day of dreams coming true.\", \"from\": 143, \"to\": 184, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So many tears of joy!\", \"from\": 185, \"to\": 206, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have a complete set of medals now, my love!\", \"from\": 207, \"to\": 254, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"the Oscar-winning screenwriter penned on Instagram.\", \"from\": 254, \"to\": 306, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 296, \"end\": 305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.949008057305232e-15, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Team GB athlete scored a silver medal in the men's synchro 10m platform alongside his diving partner, Noah Williams.\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 414, \"end\": 427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"score\": 0.999998273608197, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nobody seemed prouder of Tom than his son, Robbie, six, who was seen cheering on his dad on the sidelines alongside his little brother Phoenix, 18 months.\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 473, \"end\": 479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"score\": 0.9994846927449457, \"rank\": 0.00046114894185082605, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\"}, {\"begin\": 565, \"end\": 572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.9961689568414248, \"rank\": 0.003813071122106637, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In case you missed it, Tom's adorable supporters wore T-shirts emblazoned with 'Team Daley' on the front and 'THAT'S MY PAPA!'\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 712, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"on the back.\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 725, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Robbie, who has a full head of golden blonde hair, proudly waved a Union Jack flag and was later seen wrapped in a large Great Britain flag as his dad took to the podium.\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 897, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 727, \"end\": 733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"score\": 0.9994846927449457, \"rank\": 0.00046114894185082605, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\"}, {\"begin\": 848, \"end\": 861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999414174153947, \"rank\": 2.0016392607964686e-05, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Tom ticked off his fifth Olympic appearance 16 years after first competing in Beijing aged 14, he did so in honour of his eldest son, Robbie.\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 1043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 980, \"end\": 987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999948369251388, \"rank\": 5.1631013883259155e-06, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1036, \"end\": 1042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"score\": 0.9994846927449457, \"rank\": 0.00046114894185082605, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been a little over 16 months since our eldest son, Robbie, shared with Tom that he wished he could watch his Papa dive in the Olympics in person,\\\" Dustin penned on Instagram.\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1102, \"end\": 1108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"score\": 0.9994846927449457, \"rank\": 0.00046114894185082605, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\"}, {\"begin\": 1215, \"end\": 1224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.949008057305232e-15, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are so proud of Tom for all of the sacrifices and incredibly hard work he's put in to get to his 5th Olympics and to make Robbie's wish come true!\\\"\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1376, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1351, \"end\": 1357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"score\": 0.9994846927449457, \"rank\": 0.00046114894185082605, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a post-dive interview, Tom spoke of his decision to return to the competitive sport after floating the idea of retirement two years ago.\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think most of that [decision] was being able to set an example to my kids that if you have a dream and you work hard, it does not mean that you are always going to be able to achieve exactly what you want to, but it's about enjoying the process and doing what you can to show up, to be the best person that you can be.\\\"\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The doting dad added: \\\"For me, this year is the happiest I have been in diving because diving wasn't necessarily my top priority.\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1972, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Of course, it was extremely important.\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 2013, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But there is nothing more important than my children and being able to spend time with them.\\\"\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2107, \"entities\": []}]}"